FBIS4-41940 "drsov125_r_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-125 Daily Report 28 Jun 1994 Azerbaijan Finance Minister, Regional Officials Appointed Finance Minister, Regional Officials Appointed NC2806193294 Baku Azerbaycan Radio Televiziyasi Television Network in Azeri 1600 GMT 28 Jun 94 NC2806193294 Baku Azerbaycan Radio Televiziyasi Television Network Azeri BFN [Text] By a decree from the Azerbaijani president, Fikret Guseyin ogly Yusupov has been appointed finance minister of the Republic, and (Erasun) Velidzhan ogly Abbasov, president of Azergush State Industrial Enterprise. By decrees from the Azerbaijani President, Ali Bedr ogly Babayev has been appointed head of Bilasuvar Rayon Executive Authority. Vali Shukur ogly Sefiyev has been relieved from this post. Agababa Kasym Ogly Kasymov has been appointed head of Gadhzigabul Rayon Executive Authority.
